<section id="ablation">
  <h2>04. Ablation Study</h2>

  <p>Each feature flag was individually toggled to measure its isolated contribution to retrieval quality. Negative delta means the feature <strong>helps</strong> when enabled.</p>

  <h3>Feature Impact Ranking</h3>

  <div class="chart-container">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.ablation_waterfall }}" alt="Ablation waterfall" />
    <p class="chart-caption">Figure 4 — Impact of each feature on NDCG@10 when disabled. Negative bars indicate the feature improves quality.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Impact Matrix</h3>

  <div class="chart-container">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{ charts.ablation_heatmap }}" alt="Ablation heatmap" />
    <p class="chart-caption">Figure 5 — Multi-metric delta matrix. Red = quality drops when feature is disabled.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Top 10 Most Impactful Features</h3>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>Group</th>
        <th class="text-right">NDCG Delta</th>
        <th class="text-right">MRR Delta</th>
        <th class="text-right">Recall Delta</th>
        <th class="text-right">Latency Delta</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for r in ablation_top10 %}
      <tr>
        <td class="mono">{{ r.flag_name }}</td>
        <td><span class="tag">{{ r.group }}</span></td>
        <td class="mono text-right">{{ "%+.4f" | format(r.delta_ndcg) }}</td>
        <td class="mono text-right">{{ "%+.4f" | format(r.delta_mrr) }}</td>
        <td class="mono text-right">{{ "%+.4f" | format(r.delta_recall) }}</td>
        <td class="mono text-right">{{ "%+.1f" | format(r.delta_latency_ms) }}ms</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>
